Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Bixonronki, ichama onpax nachíxonki motsati iki.
Original Spanish Sentence: Luego se agrega un poco de agua y se mezcla chapeando.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Bi-xon-ronki, icha-ma onpax na-chí-xon-ki motsa-ti iki.

Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja pekáo-ronki, chosko tepi yochi bi-xon ne-tosh-ti iki.

Original Spanish Sentence: Esto se tiene que hacer por la mañanita, para que el perro sea buen cazador.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Nato-ronki no-n a-ti iki yamékiri-res, ochíti mecha a-ti kopí.

Original Spanish Sentence: Después agarramos al perro que queremos curar y le amarramos las patas con una soga.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja pekáo-ronki, ja ochíti no-n mecha a-kas-ai-bo-ki yatan-ti iki nishi-n,ta-nex-nonxon.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Bixonronki, kenati iki westíora joni, jan ochíti yatankinti.

Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Bi-xon-ronki, kena-ti iki westíora joni, ja-n ochíti yatan-kin-ti.

Original Spanish Sentence: Esta persona aprieta al animal entre sus piernas.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Jo-ke-tian, bitaxma-ti iki kishi-nko.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jaskáribixonra, non jawen kishibo tashkanxon nexati atipanke jiwiki.
Original Spanish Sentence: De igual manera podemos poner al perro patas arriba y amarrarle las patas a un palo.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-ská-ribi-xon-ra, no-n jawen kishi-bo tashka-n-xon nexa-ti atipan-ke jiwi-ki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jatian, ja repoaitonin benkex poyaman maponko yatantaana, westa mekeman waxmen bixon raonko pokotaana ochíti repoti iki, rabé rekin kininkobi.
Original Spanish Sentence: Mientras, la persona encargada de curar al perro (en la nariz) le sujeta la cabeza con una mano, con la otra mano remoja el algodón en el remedio previamente preparado y lo echa en las fosas nasales del perro.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-tian, ja repo-ai-tonin benkex poyaman mapo-nko yatan-taana, westa mekeman waxmen bi-xon rao-nko poko-taan-a ochíti repo-ti iki, rabé rekin kini-nko-bi.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Axon yatantaana, boxon jeneki potati iki, nashinon ixon.
Original Spanish Sentence: Después se lleva al perro a la orilla del rioy se le bota al agua para quse se bañe.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: A-xon yatan-taana, bo-xon jene-ki pota-ti iki, nashi-non i-xon.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Westíora nete winómaxon, kachio boti iki xetemanonxon.
Original Spanish Sentence: Al día siguiente, se lleva al perro al monte para hacerlo olfatear.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Westíora nete winó-max-on, kachio bo-ti iki xete-ma-nonxon.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Boxon oina xeteaitian, rabé nete winómaxon, jakiribi repoti iki, non reken aká keshká akinribi ikaxbi kachio bokin.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Bo-xon oin-a xete-ai-tian, rabé nete winó-ma-xon, jakiribi repo-ti iki, no-n reken ak-á keshká a-kin-ribi ikaxbi kachio bo-kin.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Non boti atipanke jabicho, iamax westa ochíti mechabo betan.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: No-n bo-ti atipan-ke ja-bicho, iamax westa ochíti mecha-bo betan.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jatomeax kikini axenon yoiti iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Jato-mea-x kikin-i axe-non yoi-ti iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: ¡Taka pinon jo, jo anonx awé!
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: ¡Taka pi-non jo, jo a-nonx a-wé!

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Akin, akin, jo, jo akin.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: A-kin, a-kin, jo, jo a-kin.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: mari akin, ano akin, yawish akin, tsanas akin, mananxawe akin.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: mari a-kin, ano a-kin, yawish a-kin, tsanas a-kin, mananxawe a-kin.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Akin, akin, jo, jo akin; taka pinon jo, jo akin.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: A-kin, a-kin, jo, jo a-kin; taka pi-non jo, jo a-kin.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jara akai min jo, jo ayamaribakin, raanribikin.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-ra ak-ai mi-n jo, jo a-yama-riba-kin, raan-ribi-kin.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Akin, akin; min jo, jo ayamaitianra en mia raonribiai, mecha ochíti ikai kaman!
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: A-kin, a-kin; mi-n jo, jo a-yamai-tian-ra e-n mi-a rao-n-ribi-ai, mecha ochíti ik-ai kaman!

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jatian, ja ochítinin taka pikaskin yoina biti jake.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-tian, ja ochíti-nin taka pi-kas-kin yoina bi-ti ja-ke.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Ikaxbi ja yoinanin nami non shee axon, noe axon pitima iki; jainoax xaoribi moshatima iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ikaxbi ja yoina-nin nami no-n shee a-xon, noe a-xon pi-ti-ma iki; jainoax xao-ribi mosha-ti-ma iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jatian, nato ochítinin biti atipanke icha yoina.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-tian, nato ochíti-nin bi-ti atipan-ke icha yoina.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Non nato jawékibo senen ayamaitian, moa nato ochítinin yoinabo biamai, moa xenin ramia.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: No-n nato jawéki-bo senen a-yamai-tian, moa nato ochíti-nin yoina-bo biamai, moa xeni-n rami-a.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Nato raobaon ochíti raonaronki biai: mari, ano, yawish, tsanas, mananxawe.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Nato rao-baon ochíti rao-n-a-ronki bi-ai: mari, ano, yawish, tsanas, mananxawe.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jatíres iki, iráke. Jaskárai maton kaibo.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Jatí-res iki, iráke. Ja-ská-rai mato-n kai-bo.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jawetianbira non rayos yoyo ayosma iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Jawe-tian-bi-ra no-n rayos yoyo a-yosma iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Non beneitsa jisáma iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: No-n bene-itsa jis-á-ma iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jawetianbi non jowé ranon! ayosma iki, Xontá, jonon min bene!, akin akai.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Jawe-tian-bi no-n jo-wé ranon! a-yosma iki, Xontá, jo-non mi-n bene!, a-kin ak-ai.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jatian jawen rayos jee, jee ikai, Jatian bakeranomanbiribi titia jonon Birí, akin akai.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-tian jawen rayos jee, jee ik-ai, Jatian bake-ranoman-bi-ribi titia jo-non Birí, a-kin ak-ai.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jatian joo ikai.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Jatian joo ik-ai.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Ramakamanbi noa non rayos betan yoyo iamaai, noa jaskara iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Rama-kaman-bi no-a no-n rayos betan yoyo i-ama-ai, no-a ja-ska-ra iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Wetsankobo kaaibi non oin oinresai non rayos.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Wetsa-nko-bo ka-ai-bi no-n oin oin-res-ai no-n rayos.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Non jawe ikemein, non bene ikemein rayos non yokáti iki; jakonshoko akinres non rayos ati jake.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: No-n jawe i-ke-mein, no-n bene i-ke-mein rayos no-n yoká-ti iki; jakon-shoko a-kin-res no-n rayos a-ti ja-ke.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Ramatian, ochó katanketian: Mia joá, chakí? Mia joá, baké?, non jawékiamaai non bakebi keskáakin.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Rama-tian, ochó ka-tan-ke-tian: Mi-a jo-á, chakí? Mi-a jo-á, baké?, no-n jawéki-a-ma-ai no-n bake-bi keská-a-kin.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Moatian akátikanai, yoyo ayamabireskin, pataxbobi winoyamakatikanai non rayos.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Moa-tian a-káti-kan-ai, yoyo a-yama-bires-kin, patax-bo-bi wino-yama-kati-kan-ai no-n rayos.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Rama jaskarama iki, rama non winotaniai, pataxtanibo noa niai.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Rama ja-ska-ra-ma iki, rama no-n wino-tani-ai, patax-tani-bo no-a ni-ai.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Moatian jaskarama ikátiai; moa jawen rayos ochó joai oinax beokatikanai, jawen rayos beisnaketian.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Moa-tian ja-ska-ra-ma i-káti-ai; moa jawen rayos ochó jo-ai oin-ax beo-kati-kan-ai, jawen rayos be-is-na-ke-tian.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jaskarabo ikátikanai.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-ska-ra-bo i-káti-kan-ai.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jawetianki jawen bakeya iki, jatianpari yoyo akátikanai.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Jawe-tian-ki jawen bake-ya iki, ja-tian-pari yoyo a-káti-kan-ai.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jain jawen bake iketianpari: Min benen bakishpari jaskara atánon!
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Jain jawen bake i-ke-tian-pari: Mi-n bene-n bakish-pari ja-ska-ra a-tánon!

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jatian rayos kaai yomeraaibo, nonti akíbo, winti akíbo.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-tian rayos ka-ai yomera-ai-bo, nonti ak-í-bo, winti ak-í-bo.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Rama kamanbi ja axébo noa keyotama iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Rama kaman-bi ja axé-bo noa keyo-t-a-ma iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Nokon rayos ochokeax joaitian en yoyo ayamaai, ponté en jowé aresai.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Nokon rayos ochokea-x jo-ai-tian e-n yoyo a-yama-ai, ponté e-n jo-wé a-res-ai.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Nokon jawe ikemein mia joa? ixon metsonboti iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Nokon jawe i-ke-mein mi-a jo-a? i-xon me-tson-bo-ti iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jatian jawen awin joai mia joa?, akin akai; mia joa? axon jan bibainai.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-tian jawen awin jo-ai mi-a jo-a?, a-kin ak-ai; mi-a jo-a? a-xon ja-n bi-bain-ai.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Non jaskáati atipanyamake, shiroma iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: No-n ja-ská-a-ti atipan-yama-ke, shiro-ma iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jatian yoyo akinmabi jan jawékibo bea moa non akai.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-tian yoyo a-kin-ma-bi ja-n jawéki-bo be-a moa no-n ak-ai.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jatian ja jonin onanke: nokon rayosenra ea noike ixon.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-tian ja joni-n onan-ke: nokon rayos-en-ra e-a noi-ke i-xon.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Joketian, non xeamayamakin oinresa bakeranoman shinanai: Nokon rayosenra ea noiyamake, ikai.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Jo-ke-tian, no-n xea-ma-yama-kin oin-res-a bake-ranoman shinan-ai: Nokon rayos-en-ra e-a noi-yama-ke, ik-ai.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jaskara itima iki, jatíxonbi noiti jake.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-ska-ra i-ti-ma iki, jatí-xon-bi noi-ti ja-ke.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Nokon jane riki Inkan Soi.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Nokon jane r-iki Inkan Soi.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Ea riki Bawanixonkonia.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: E-a r-iki Bawanixo-nko-ni-a.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Enra mato yoiai westíora nokon yosishokobetan ea winóni jawéki, yomerai kaax.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: E-n-ra mato yoi-ai westíora nokon yosi-shoko-betan e-a winó-ni jawéki, yomera-i ka-ax.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Westíora netenra kaa iki nokon yosi betan ea, piti benai; piti benai kaa iki noa ianman.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Westíora nete-n-ra ka-a iki nokon yosi betan e-a, piti bena-i; piti bena-i ka-a iki no-a ian-man.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jenetian iketian noa Paron pikota iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Jene-tian i-ke-tian no-a Paro-n piko-t-a iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Paron pikotax noa kaa iki iná inati.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Paro-n piko-t-ax no-a ka-a iki iná inat-i.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Kakin non natsá natasábaina iki, natsá natsábaina iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ka-kin no-n na-tsá na-tasá-bain-a iki, na-tsá na-tsá-bain-a iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Kakin casi kimisha mayá pekáo, moa non jawebi ayama pekáo, moa noa jatsana iká iki, yantanpaketainribi, nokon yosishoko en yoia iki: Ramabi non jawe akai akin yokata iká iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ka-kin casi kimisha mayá pekáo, moa no-n jawe-bi a-yama pekáo, moa no-a jatsan-a ik-á iki, yantan-paket-ai-n-ribi, nokon yosi-shoko e-n yoi-a iki: Rama-bi no-n jawe ak-ai a-kin yokat-a ik-á iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jaskarabi noa kati jaai, babá akin aká iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-ska-ra-bi no-a ka-ti ja-ai, babá a-kin ak-á iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Ja noa joa iki, jakiribi moa toxbápaketi.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja no-a jo-a iki, jakiribi moa toxbá-paket-i.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jokin non oina taxa tsamata iká iki, nato joxo manxan tsamata.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Jo-kin no-n oin-a taxa tsama-t-a ik-á iki, nato joxo manxan tsama-t-a.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jatian joxo manxan tsamata iketian, en oinama iketian, ja nokon papashokon ea yoia iki: Babá, oara joxo manxan tsamáke.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-tian joxo manxan tsama-t-a i-ke-tian, e-n oin-a-ma i-ke-tian, ja nokon papa-shoko-n e-a yoi-a iki: Babá, oa-ra joxo manxan tsamá-ke.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jatian en oina iká iki ochócha mayá pekáo, mayá pekáoirama paboronin, joxo manxan, kimisha joxo manxan.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-tian e-n oin-a ik-á iki ochó-cha mayá pekáo, mayá pekáo-ira-ma paboro-nin, joxo manxan, kimisha joxo manxan.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Netéshaman noa toxbápaketa iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Neté-shaman no-a toxbá-paket-a iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jainxon ea neri ea winaxonwe, babashoko akin aká iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Jain-xon e-a ne-ri e-a wina-xon-we, baba-shoko a-kin ak-á iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jaskáyamawe! Jabi ea neri axonwe.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-ská-yama-we! Ja-bi e-a ne-ri a-xon-we.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jatian neri en winaxona, yoiakeskábi, yosi kikin mecha iká iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-tian ne-ri e-n wina-xon-a, yoi-a-keská-bi, yosi kikin mecha ik-á iki.

Original Shipibo-Conibo Sentence: Jayáshoko ja abeiranI noa joa iki.
Shipibo-Conibo Morphological Segmentatio: Ja-yá-shoko ja a-beiran-I no-a jo-a iki.
